iate scoring, complete answer explanations, and an individualized analysis of your results.  In addition, you will find interactive popular software tutorials/courses that are video-based and allow you to learn at your own pace.</li></ul>', 'Change My Career', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '27-revision-14', '', '', '2012-06-12 20:23:33', '2012-06-12 20:23:33', '', 27, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/27-revision-14/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
