(137, 2, '2012-06-11 18:29:25', '2012-06-11 18:29:25', '<h1>Change My Career</h1>\r\nThe majority of us have multiple careers during our lifetimes.  If you’re considering making a change, we’ve compiled some resources to help.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.mainecareercenter.com/employment/training-adults/index.shtml" target="_blank">Maine’s Career Centers</a> are a great place to start assessing what your next step might be. They can provide information about how to decide what career is right for you, and how to get the right training to be qualified. To see the full list of career center locations <a href="http://www.mainecareercenter.com/locations/index.shtml" target="_blank">Click here</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.maine.gov/labor/labor_stats/jobs_in_demand.shtml" target="_blank">Jobs in demand in Maine</a> provides a list of job fields around Maine that are desired by employers.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.mainecareercenter.com/employment/search/index.shtml" target="_blank">The Maine Job Bank</a> also has a list of jobs around the state of Maine that are desired by employers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Skill Improvement and Certification Exam Prep:</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.maine.gov/msl/commons/learnexp/index.shtml" target="_blank">LearningExpress Library</a> is offered by the Maine State Library and features over 770 practice tests, tutorials, and eBooks related to job search and workplace skills improvement, career certification and licensing exam preparation, college entrance and graduate school admissions exam preparation, GED exam preparation, and basic skills improvement in reading, writing, and math, for all ages.\r\n\r\nYou will get immediate scoring, complete answer explanations, and an individualized analysis of your results.  In addition, you will find interactive popular software tutorials/courses that are video-based and allow you to learn at your own pace.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>DEGREES &amp; CERTIFICATES</h2>\r\nBrowse 2 or 4 year degree programs, certificates or advanced degrees available in Maine that might qualify you for the career you really <em>want</em>.\r\nAssociates Degrees (2 Year)\r\nBachelors Degrees (4 Year)\r\nCertificates\r\nAdvanced Degrees', 'Change My Career', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '27-revision-12', '', '', '2012-06-11 18:29:25', '2012-06-11 18:29:25', '', 27, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/27-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
