(5620, 1, '2012-09-10 19:29:08', '2012-09-10 19:29:08', 'Many of the 80+ adult education programs in Maine offer GED prep courses to help you prepare for the test. These classes are free. Search for your local adult education program or browse classes <a title="Maine Adult Education" href="http://msad9.maineadulted.org/" target="_blank">here</a>.\n\nAlthough you can’t take the Maine GED online currently, you can study online. There are various sites available with study guides, prep tests and other information. For example, Many of these sites charge a membership fee or fees for pre-tests, so screen them carefully or get advice from your local adult education provider about your options.', 'How can I prepare for the test?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2398-autosave', '', '', '2012-09-10 19:29:08', '2012-09-10 19:29:08', '', 2398, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/2398-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
