(6028, 1, '2012-10-01 15:39:24', '2012-10-01 15:39:24', 'The GED<sup>&reg;</sup> test is the high school equivalency degree. The GED<sup>&reg;</sup> test is actually the process of earning the equivalent of your high school diploma, which is called a GED<sup>&reg;</sup> test certificate or credential. What is the GED<sup>&reg;</sup> te, really? It''s a chance to feel a great sense of accomplishment. It''s one step on the path to college and greater opportunity for yourself and your family.', 'What is the GED<sup>&reg;</sup> test?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2393-autosave', '', '', '2012-10-01 15:39:24', '2012-10-01 15:39:24', '', 2393, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/2393-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
