(6895, 1, '2013-04-15 13:54:00', '2013-04-15 13:54:00', 'The Bachelor of Science in Criminal Justice prepares learners for an exciting and challenging career in the rapidly expanding fields of law enforcement, corrections, probation, and private sector fields. Undergraduate students in this program may choose from a wide range of internships and attend the Maine Criminal Justice Academy in their senior year to pursue certification to become eligible for employment as a full-time law enforcement officer upon graduation.', 'Criminal Justice', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'criminal-justice-4', '', '', '2013-04-15 13:54:00', '2013-04-15 13:54:00', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/criminal-justice-4/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
