(7177, 1, '2013-04-15 13:59:15', '2013-04-15 13:59:15', 'The Department of New Media at the University of Maine offers an interdisciplinary course of study in the systems, technologies, history, art, design, and theory of information artifacts and networks. The curriculum enables students to investigate the creative and applied processes essential to this area of study. It prepares students to be technologically capable innovators, articulate thinkers, and creative new media developers.', 'New Media', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-media', '', '', '2013-04-15 13:59:15', '2013-04-15 13:59:15', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/new-media/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
