(7184, 1, '2013-04-15 13:59:23', '2013-04-15 13:59:23', 'Philosophy is a discipline devoted to rigorous reflection on human nature, culture and the world.  Courses are available in the History of Western Philosophy, Buddhism and Hinduism, political philosophy, areas of applied ethics like medical and environmental ethics, logic, existentialism and phenomenology, and feminist philosophy.  The program prepares students interested in graduate school, but is also a respected gateway major for those interested in law, business, government, or education.  The Department also offers two minors.', 'Philosophy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'philosophy', '', '', '2013-04-15 13:59:23', '2013-04-15 13:59:23', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/philosophy/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
