(7243, 1, '2013-04-15 14:00:39', '2013-04-15 14:00:39', 'Three minors are available for University of Maine students wishing to complement their studies in other disciplines with some exposure to business.  At least 50% of the courses must be taken at UMaine. Declare your minor in the Undergraduate Office (DPC 211) of the Maine Business School.  Students must have a GPA of 2.0 at the University of Maine in order to declare a minor and must earn a 2.0 accumulative GPA or better in the minor’s courses in order for the minor to appear on their transcript.', 'Business Administration', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'business-administration-16', '', '', '2013-04-15 14:00:39', '2013-04-15 14:00:39', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/business-administration-16/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
