(7290, 1, '2013-04-15 14:01:37', '2013-04-15 14:01:37', 'The Maine Studies minor allows students to follow an interdisciplinary study of Maine. The program consists of 18 credit hours, including two required courses: MES 101, Into to Maine Studies, and MES 201, The Maine Coast. Students select the remaining 12 credits from interdisciplinary and discipline-based Maine-focused courses. See complete list of courses applicable to the Maine Studies minor at http://www.umaine.edu/mainestudies/', 'Maine Studies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'maine-studies', '', '', '2013-04-15 14:01:37', '2013-04-15 14:01:37', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/maine-studies/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
(7291, 1, '2013-04-15 14:01:39', '2013-04-15 14:01:39', 'Three minors are available for University of Maine students wishing to complement their studies in other disciplines with some exposure to business.  At least 50% of the courses must be taken at UMaine. Declare your minor in the Undergraduate Office (DPC 211) of the Maine Business School.  Students must have a GPA of 2.0 at the University of Maine in order to declare a minor and must earn a 2.0 accumulative GPA or better in the minor’s courses in order for the minor to appear on their transcript.', 'Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'management', '', '', '2013-04-15 14:01:39', '2013-04-15 14:01:39', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/management/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
(7292, 1, '2013-04-15 14:01:40', '2013-04-15 14:01:40', 'The Marxist and Socialist Studies minor consists of 18 credits and is an interdisciplinary program with a required course on Marxist Philosophy offered by the Philosophy Department.  This minor encourages students to study a variety of Marxist and Socialst perspectives that challenge the idea that capitalist values are "natural," "according to human nature," or inevitable .  Core courses are offered by Philosophy, Economics, English, and History.  Elective courses are offered by an even wider range of programs.', 'Marxist And Socialist Studies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'marxist-and-socialist-studies', '', '', '2013-04-15 14:01:40', '2013-04-15 14:01:40', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/marxist-and-socialist-studies/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
