(7323, 1, '2013-04-15 14:02:20', '2013-04-15 14:02:20', 'Our goals are to prepare University of Maine students to successfully take their places in the new global century. We offer courses that teach the past – with Latin and Classical Studies, as well as the present with French, German, and Spanish studies that address both the cultural and literary heritages of these languages. We also offer current courses in conversation and composition, film, North American French, as well as other courses applicable to the present.', 'Spanish', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'spanish-3', '', '', '2013-04-15 14:02:20', '2013-04-15 14:02:20', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/spanish-3/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
