(7540, 1, '2013-04-15 14:07:25', '2013-04-15 14:07:25', 'The Bachelor of Applied Science degree is designed to help students who have earned an associate''s degree in the trade and technical areas to pursue a bachelor''s degree that complements and incorporates their prior college work.', 'Physical Science', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'physical-science', '', '', '2013-04-15 14:07:25', '2013-04-15 14:07:25', '', 0, 'http://www.nextstepmaine.org/program/physical-science/', 0, 'nsm_program', '', 0),
